<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="1356" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="17.[178,1085,935,1134]" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356">
This group is here established for four Melanesian species, 
<emphasis box="[796,923,936,958]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356">S. aequatum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="LOBL I." box="[931,1054,935,958]" journalOrPublisher="Revue suisse Zool" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356" pagination="3 - 69" part="84" refString="LOBL I. (1977 a): Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) Australiens. - Revue suisse Zool. 84: 3 - 69." title="Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) Australiens" type="journal article" year="1977">LÖBL, 1977</bibRefCitation>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356">S. distans</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="LOBL I." box="[258,380,964,987]" journalOrPublisher="Revue suisse Zool" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356" pagination="3 - 69" part="84" refString="LOBL I. (1977 a): Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) Australiens. - Revue suisse Zool. 84: 3 - 69." title="Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) Australiens" type="journal article" year="1977">LÖBL, 1977</bibRefCitation>
, 
<emphasis box="[392,522,966,987]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356">S. tannaense</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="LOBL I." box="[530,650,964,987]" journalOrPublisher="Mitt. schweiz. ent. Ges" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356" pagination="53 - 57" part="51" refString="LOBL I. (1978 a): Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Gattung Sapitia ACHARD (Coleoptera, Scaphidiidae). - Mitt. schweiz. ent. Ges. 51: 53 - 57." title="Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Gattung Sapitia ACHARD (Coleoptera, Scaphidiidae)" type="journal article" year="1978">LÖBL, 1978</bibRefCitation>
and 
<emphasis box="[702,867,966,987]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356">S. zimmermanni</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="LOBL I." box="[875,998,964,987]" journalOrPublisher="Revue suisse Zool" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356" pagination="3 - 69" part="84" refString="LOBL I. (1977 a): Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) Australiens. - Revue suisse Zool. 84: 3 - 69." title="Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) Australiens" type="journal article" year="1977">LÖBL, 1977</bibRefCitation>
, and the new Philippine 
<emphasis box="[345,468,995,1016]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356">S. diversum</emphasis>
described below (see 
<bibRefCitation author="LOBL I." box="[709,839,993,1017]" journalOrPublisher="Revue suisse Zool" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356" pagination="817 - 829" part="84" refString="LOBL I. (1977 b): Wenig bekannte und neue Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) von Neukaledonien, Samoa und von den Fidschiinseln. - Revue suisse Zool. 84: 817 - 829." title="Wenig bekannte und neue Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) von Neukaledonien, Samoa und von den Fidschiinseln" type="journal article" year="1977" yearSuffix="b">LÖBL 1977b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="LOBL I." box="[852,920,995,1017]" journalOrPublisher="Pacific Insects" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356" pagination="109 - 111" part="19" refString="LOBL I. (1978 b): Two new Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) from the New Hebrides. - Pacific Insects 19: 109 - 111." title="Two new Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) from the New Hebrides" type="journal article" year="1978" yearSuffix="b">1978b</bibRefCitation>
). These species have symmetrical aedeagi with long, narrow parameres each bearing a small apical membranous lobe. The internal sac is simple, with a flagellum. The New Guinean 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356">S. dissimile</emphasis>
LÖBL, 1975 and 
<emphasis box="[456,566,1083,1104]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356">S. papuum</emphasis>
(LÖBL, 1975) and the Mascarene 
<emphasis box="[930,1021,1083,1104]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356">S. gomyi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="LOBL I." journalOrPublisher="Revue suisse Zool" pageId="17" pageNumber="1356" pagination="3 - 69" part="84" refString="LOBL I. (1977 a): Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) Australiens. - Revue suisse Zool. 84: 3 - 69." title="Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) Australiens" type="journal article" year="1977">Löbl, 1977</bibRefCitation>
possesse similar aedeagi but differs drastically in other characters.
</paragraph>
